{"tid":1554958,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"枉死案  關鍵錄影離奇全黑　動手腳刪掉「誰」？","createTime":"2019-09-09T07:31:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T08:34:48.000Z","uid":29917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a0abd5de79e4cbfdf3cacfd3c1d4b5732346aba","tid":1554958,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:31:02.000Z","msg":"洪仲丘關鍵錄影離奇全黑 動手腳刪掉「誰」？<br />\n<br />\nETtoday政治 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20130721/244375.htm#ixzz5z0iH9lHF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20130721%2F244375.htm%23ixzz5z0iH9lHF&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kajPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=5ca16725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20130721/244375.htm#ixzz5z0iH9lHF</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook<br />\n<br />\n陸軍542旅下士洪仲丘枉死案，關鍵錄影畫面經還原竟然「全黑」，家屬認為，錄影有消失必定有人刪除，洪母則透露，「早有人告知畫面遭人動過手腳。」<br />\n<br />\n最高軍檢署檢察長曹金生昨天出面說明「消失的80分鐘」還原結果：第一，監視器畫面都在，沒有被刪除；第二，16個鏡頭都非人為刪除；第三，16個鏡頭若拔除電源，畫面會全黑，但檔案並無全黑，16個鏡頭為何陸續停止動作，專案小組會秉持軍人奮戰到底的精神繼續追查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/354/d354254.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F354%2Fd354254.jpg&h=b31e84db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對軍高檢指監視錄影沒有人為操作，洪仲丘的母親胡素真表示不可思議、太誇張，認為這只會把議題愈搞愈大。洪仲丘姊姊洪慈庸(上圖)說，根據禁閉生私下告訴他們的真相是，「影片已遭人弄掉了」，當天仲丘的操練雖然很正常，但范佐憲卻無故出現在禁閉營區中，「誰」出現在畫面中讓軍方不能公布？<br />\n<br />\n洪慈庸直言，黑畫面是「人為所致」，所以無法還原畫面，家屬提出證據保全，卻未獲正面回應，現在已不相信軍方、檢方，調查希望能有第三方介入。<br />\n<br />\n民進黨立委陳亭妃痛批，連3歲小孩都知道這是人為所致。她表示，陸軍有規定，戰情官每2小時要記錄一次監視器的情況，有問題要立即回報，同時登載進「戰情日誌」，出現這麼長時間的黑畫面，「戰情官有可能沒看到、沒記錄嗎？」如果國軍渙散到連監視器故障都沒警覺，這是比洪仲丘遭虐死更嚴重的營安危機。"},{"pid":"11376b3d05bb59c393150be6017febf9e7e1b63f","tid":1554958,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc1de6a229c7f4336bb81f3f922520fc4a1b1f0","tid":1554958,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393408466ee46d3ddb28c6b55e96ca4c94737b75","tid":1554958,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}